text: Dapcha Kashikhanda is municipality in Kavrepalanchok District in Bagmati Pradesh of central Nepal. It is located about 6 kilometres southeast of the district headquarters of Dhulikhel. This place is formed by combination of 6 previous village development committeeshttp://ddckavre.gov.np/en/ namely Mathurapati, Methinkot, Puranogaun, Chhatrebanjh, Daraune Pokhari and Khanalthok. ==References== Category:Populated places in Kavrepalanchok District
title: Dapcha Kashikhanda
